в”ңв”Җname_path=c2
в””в”Җexpr=
  в””в”ҖFunctionCall(GoogleSQL:concat(STRING, repeated(1) STRING) -> STRING)
    в”ңв”ҖConstant(c1, type=STRING, value="abcdef")
    в””в”ҖLiteral(type=STRING, value="!")

Constant registered.
Constant evaluated.
